data.description: Welcome to your new abode at 512 Grant Avenue, located in the tranquil neighborhood of Willow Grove, PA. This exquisite home boasts custom craftsmanship and is conveniently situated near major highways, local shops, and restaurants. As you enter through the grand 2-story foyer, you'll be greeted by a spacious formal living room, accompanied by a cozy office space ideal for remote work or a children's playroom.  The expansive sunken living room features a captivating stone gas fireplace and a spiral staircase that leads to the second-floor deck. Adjacent to this, step up to the elegant dining room, which provides access to the vast backyard and a stunning stone patio. Hardwood flooring gracefully flows throughout the interior, enhancing the overall charm of the home.  Prepare culinary delights in the beautifully designed eat-in kitchen, adorned with tiled floors and backsplash, 42' cabinets, an island, and two sinks. Conveniently, the kitchen also offers access to the one-car garage and a massive unfinished basement, providing ample storage space or potential for customization.  Upstairs, you'll discover the oversized owner's suite featuring a generously sized walk-in closet and an enormous en suite bathroom, which was tastefully updated just six months ago. French doors off the owner's suite lead to the second-floor deck, offering a private retreat. Additionally, there are two well-proportioned bedrooms and an updated hall bath showcasing a stunning tiled shower with an adjustable showerhead. Completing the second floor is brand new carpeting and a laundry room for added convenience.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this splendid residence your own, with its thoughtful design, desirable location, and modern updates. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm and comfort of 512 Grant Avenue.
